headline: MetLife Pet Insurance Honors "The Bond Between" with the Golden Beagle Award for Outstanding Animal Welfare Contributions
summary: NEW YORK, October 14, 2025--MetLife Pet Insurance and the Association of Animal Welfare Advancement are pleased to announce that the Minnetonka-based organization The Bond Between is the recipient of the second annual Golden Beagle Award. The organization is being recognized for their outstanding contributions to animal welfare, including their work fostering the bond between humans and animals and providing essential services to prevent animal homelessness.
